description: This file is the entry point for a React.js web application. It imports React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component. It initializes the React application by rendering the App component inside the DOM element with id 'root' under React's StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering a React component into the specified DOM node.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the created root.
